title: Nearly 5 years after Uri, ERCOT says Texas power grid will be stable this winter
description: The Texas grid operator found that under most weather conditions, there is a less than 2% chance of a grid emergency through February. However, Texas could be in trouble in the unlikely event that a repeat of the 2021 freeze hits large parts of the state.

title: 400 jobs to be cut at Natural Resources Canada by 2029
description: Approximately 400 positions will be cut at Natural Resources Canada (NRCan) over the next four years, as part of the federal government’s Comprehensive Expenditure Review to find $60 billion in savings.

title: Braves To Sign Aaron Schunk To Minor League Deal
description: The Braves will have infielder Aaron Schunk in camp as a non-roster invitee, reports Gabe Burns of the Atlanta Journal-Constitution. That indicates the CAA Sports client and the club have agreed to a minor league deal.
